973/*



974 * Output and update for atomic system:



975 *    '<S41>/Trigger Hold'



976 *    '<S52>/Trigger Hold'



977 */



978void LCK_TriggerHold(boolean_T rtu_Trigger, real32_T rtu_hold_time,



979                     B_TriggerHold_LCK_T *localB)



980{



981  boolean_T guard1 = false;



982



983  /* Chart: '<S41>/Trigger Hold' */



984  guard1 = false;



985  if (rtu_Trigger) {



986    localB->count = 0.0F;



987    guard1 = true;



988  } else if ((localB->count <= rtu_hold_time) && (localB->count > 0.0F)) {



989    guard1 = true;



990  } else {



991    localB->Out = false;



992  }



993



994  if (guard1) {



995    localB->Out = true;



996    localB->count += ML_TIME_MSEC;



997  }



998



999  /* End of Chart: '<S41>/Trigger Hold' */



1000}

1065/*



1066 * Output and update for atomic system:



1067 *    '<S51>/Delay_Trig'



1068 *    '<S174>/Delay_Trig'



1069 *    '<S177>/Delay_Trig'



1070 *    '<S182>/Delay_Trig'



1071 *    '<S184>/Delay_Trig'



1072 *    '<S185>/Delay_Trig'



1073 *    '<S186>/Delay_Trig'



1074 *    '<S187>/Delay_Trig'



1075 *    '<S188>/Delay_Trig'



1076 *    '<S189>/Delay_Trig'



1077 *    ...



1078 */



1079void LCK_Delay_Trig(real32_T rtu_Input, real32_T rtu_Delay_Trig_Time,



1080                    B_Delay_Trig_LCK_T *localB, DW_Delay_Trig_LCK_T *localDW)



1081{



1082  /* Chart: '<S51>/Delay_Trig' */



1083  if (localDW->is_active_c1_LateralControl_fcn == 0U) {



1084    localDW->is_active_c1_LateralControl_fcn = 1U;



1085    localDW->is_c1_LateralControl_fcns_lib = LCK_IN_OFF;



1086    localB->Delay_Trig = 0.0F;



1087    localDW->duration = 0.0F;



1088  } else {



1089    switch (localDW->is_c1_LateralControl_fcns_lib) {



1090     case LCK_IN_OFF:



1091      localB->Delay_Trig = 0.0F;



1092      if (rtu_Input != 0.0F) {



1093        localDW->is_c1_LateralControl_fcns_lib = LCK_IN_ON;



1094        localB->Delay_Trig = 0.0F;



1095        localDW->duration += ML_TIME_SEC;



1096      }



1097      break;



1098



1099     case LCK_IN_ON:



1100      localB->Delay_Trig = 0.0F;



1101      if ((rtu_Input != 0.0F) && (localDW->duration >= rtu_Delay_Trig_Time)) {



1102        localDW->is_c1_LateralControl_fcns_lib = LCK_IN_Trig;



1103        localB->Delay_Trig = 1.0F;

1501/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S231>/Path_Planning_Function ' */



1502static real_T LCK_find_valid_ref_max_len(const real_T reference[800])



1503{



1504  real_T len_valid;



1505  boolean_T x[400];



1506  int32_T idx;



1507  int32_T b_ii;



1508  boolean_T exitg1;



1509  for (idx = 0; idx < 400; idx++) {



1510    x[idx] = ((reference[idx] == 0.0) && (reference[400 + idx] == 0.0));



1511  }



1512



1513  idx = 0;



1514  b_ii = 0;



1515  exitg1 = false;



1516  while ((!exitg1) && (b_ii < 400)) {



1517    if (x[b_ii]) {



1518      idx++;



1519      LCK_B.ii_data[idx - 1] = (int16_T)(b_ii + 1);



1520      if (idx >= 400) {



1521        exitg1 = true;



1522      } else {



1523        b_ii++;



1524      }



1525    } else {



1526      b_ii++;



1527    }



1528  }



1529



1530  if (1 > idx) {



1531    idx = 0;



1532  }



1533



1534  if (idx == 1) {



1535    len_valid = 400.0;



1536  } else {



1537    len_valid = (real_T)LCK_B.ii_data[1] - 3.0;



1538  }



1539



1540  return len_valid;



1541}

1543/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S231>/Path_Planning_Function ' */



1544static void LCK_reference_generation(const real_T trajs_local[800], const real_T



1545  p_store[800], real_T ref_len_valid, real_T trajs_new[800])



1546{



1547  real_T theta;



1548  int32_T i;



1549  real_T tmp;



1550  memset(&trajs_new[0], 0, 800U * sizeof(real_T));



1551  for (i = 0; i < (int32_T)ref_len_valid; i++) {



1552    if (trajs_local[i] == 0.0) {



1553      theta = 0.0;



1554    } else if (1.0 + (real_T)i == 1.0) {



1555      theta = atan(trajs_local[400] / trajs_local[0]);



1556    } else {



1557      theta = atan((trajs_local[400 + i] - trajs_local[i + 399]) /



1558                   (trajs_local[i] - trajs_local[i - 1]));



1559    }



1560



1561    if ((theta > -1.5707963267948966) && (theta <= 0.0)) {



1562      tmp = sin(theta);



1563      theta = cos(theta);



1564      trajs_new[i] = p_store[400 + i] * tmp + trajs_local[i];



1565      trajs_new[400 + i] = p_store[400 + i] * theta + trajs_local[400 + i];



1566    } else if ((theta > 0.0) && (theta < 1.5707963267948966)) {



1567      tmp = sin(theta);



1568      theta = cos(theta);



1569      trajs_new[i] = trajs_local[i] - p_store[400 + i] * tmp;



1570      trajs_new[400 + i] = p_store[400 + i] * theta + trajs_local[400 + i];



1571    } else {



1572      printf("it seems that the reference line is unacceptable!");



1573      fflush(stdout);



1574    }



1575  }



1576}

1578/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S231>/Path_Planning_Function ' */



1579static void LCK_calculate_kappa_LQ2awkOm(const real_T trajs_new[800], real_T



1580  ref_len_valid, real_T kappa[400])



1581{



1582  real_T denominator_pdd;



1583  int32_T i;



1584  memset(&LCK_B.pd[0], 0, 400U * sizeof(real_T));



1585  memset(&LCK_B.pdd[0], 0, 400U * sizeof(real_T));



1586  memset(&kappa[0], 0, 400U * sizeof(real_T));



1587  for (i = 0; i < (int32_T)(ref_len_valid - 1.0); i++) {



1588    if (fabs(trajs_new[i + 1] - trajs_new[i]) <= 1.0E-5) {



1589      denominator_pdd = 1.0E-5;



1590    } else {



1591      denominator_pdd = trajs_new[i + 1] - trajs_new[i];



1592    }



1593



1594    LCK_B.pd[i] = (trajs_new[i + 401] - trajs_new[400 + i]) / denominator_pdd;



1595  }



1596



1597  LCK_B.pd[399] = LCK_B.pd[398];



1598  for (i = 0; i < (int32_T)(ref_len_valid - 2.0); i++) {



1599    denominator_pdd = (trajs_new[i + 1] - trajs_new[i]) * 0.5;



1600    if (denominator_pdd * denominator_pdd <= 0.001) {



1601      denominator_pdd = 0.001;



1602    } else {



1603      denominator_pdd = trajs_new[i + 1] - trajs_new[i];



1604      denominator_pdd *= denominator_pdd;



1605    }



1606



1607    LCK_B.pdd[i] = ((trajs_new[i + 402] - trajs_new[i + 401] * 2.0) + trajs_new



1608                    [400 + i]) / denominator_pdd;



1609  }



1610



1611  LCK_B.pdd[398] = LCK_B.pdd[397];



1612  LCK_B.pdd[399] = LCK_B.pdd[397];



1613  for (i = 0; i < (int32_T)ref_len_valid; i++) {



1614    kappa[i] = LCK_B.pdd[i] / rt_powd_snf(LCK_B.pd[i] * LCK_B.pd[i] + 1.0, 1.5);



1615  }



1616



1617  kappa[0] = kappa[1];



1618  kappa[399] = kappa[398];



1619}

1621/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S231>/Path_Planning_Function ' */



1622static void LCK_calculate_max_ref(const real_T output[3200], real_T *max_ref,



1623  real_T *valid_len)



1624{



1625  boolean_T x[400];



1626  int32_T idx;



1627  int32_T b_ii;



1628  boolean_T exitg1;



1629  for (idx = 0; idx < 400; idx++) {



1630    x[idx] = ((output[800 + idx] == 0.0) && (output[1200 + idx] == 0.0));



1631  }



1632



1633  idx = 0;



1634  b_ii = 0;



1635  exitg1 = false;



1636  while ((!exitg1) && (b_ii < 400)) {



1637    if (x[b_ii]) {



1638      idx++;



1639      LCK_B.ii_data_m[idx - 1] = (int16_T)(b_ii + 1);



1640      if (idx >= 400) {



1641        exitg1 = true;



1642      } else {



1643        b_ii++;



1644      }



1645    } else {



1646      b_ii++;



1647    }



1648  }



1649



1650  if (1 > idx) {



1651    idx = 0;



1652  }



1653



1654  if (idx == 1) {



1655    *max_ref = 400.0;



1656    *valid_len = output[1199];



1657  } else {



1658    *max_ref = (real_T)LCK_B.ii_data_m[1] - 3.0;



1659    *valid_len = output[LCK_B.ii_data_m[1] + 796];



1660  }



1661}
